com.tozny.e3db

Interface UpdateMeta

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalUpdateMeta

    public interface UpdateMeta
    Holds immutable metadata necessary to identify a record for updating.

    Consider using the LocalUpdateMeta implementation. To convert a RecordMeta, use the LocalUpdateMeta.fromRecordMeta(RecordMeta) method.
